; Coverage test for format.cc
; Test %$ with a field index that exceeds the number of expression fields
; in the primary template. Referencing %$9 when the template only has one
; expression field triggers an error.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(account)\n%/%$9\n' -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: %$ reference to a non-existent prior field
end test
